Description: The NOMI 200S is based on the late 1.6 i-TEC Covet and equipped with a NOMI CT16 Turbocharger, as well as a modified suspension and sport tires on Dreid wheels. It's paintjob and the NOMI Bumpers give the car the look it deserves. These features combined with the price made this car one of the most popular, and affordable NOMI S-Series cars ever.
